Products



        Relays, Contactors & Switches






main







Safe, Efficient, Powerful
TE relays, contactors and switches can be used anywhere — in production lines, robotics, lifts, control panels, cash machines, motion control systems, lighting, building systems, solar, HVAC, cars, trucks, buses, off-road vehicles and an array of safety-critical applications. Our circuit breakers, relays, switches and knobs are cost-effective, reliable and enhance productivity. High-performance types are designed to withstand extreme shock, vibration, temperature and altitude.




